quote:
My father died
intestate and left two sons, my brother and myself;
I claim a share in his estate by the law of nations.

note.#text:
See v. x. 2, and again, for greater detail, v. xiv. 1 (note
at end), where an example of this type of  is given
from the  (ch. 29)

p.#text:
Words of different meaning may likewise be
grouped together, as for instance, ;
or again, as in the following passage from Ovid,

hi.#text:
Si, quantum in
agro locisque desertis audacia potest, tantum in foro atque
iudiciis impudentia valeret;
